Flaming Grill are part of The Great British Pub Card. Our Flaming Grill pubs are simply made for fun all-round. First and foremost, creating ‘flaming great steaks’ is our passion. Our steaks are always 35 days matured and served on our sizzling skillets. Best of all, with our Flaming Guarantee, if you don’t love it, we’ll replace it.  The Great British Pub Card is the leading pub gift card that can be redeemed against food, drink or accommodation in over 3000 locations nationwide. Including brands such as Chef & Brewer, Loch Fyne, Flaming Grill, Hungry Horse and many others. The Great British Pub Card is also available to purchase as a digital code, its flexible and offers a vast choice of food, drink or dining opportunities. Perfect for celebrating those special times with family, catching-up with friends or meeting with colleagues. For more information visit www.greatbritishpubcard.co.uk.